  "texts": [
    "We define accuracy and consistency as key performance metrics in this experiment.",
    "The assessment is conducted by employing four distinct prompting techniques: 1) Zero Shot prompting (ZS), 2) Chain of Thought (CoT), 3) Chain of Thought with Self Consistency (CoT-SC), and 4) Retrieval Augmented Prompting (RAP) enabled by external nutrition knowledge.",
    "The responses are then analyzed, by comparing them to the ground truth, to evaluate the performance of each LLM and prompting technique.",
    "We perform inter-rater and intra-rater analysis to identify the strengths and weaknesses of each approach.",
    "In the following, we, first, provide more details about the RD exam."
  ],
